observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor instruct the:

  - Acting GSO to conduct the physical count of all inventories of the Municipality,
prepare and submit immediately the inventory report (RPCI) thereon; and
maintain the stock cards for the inventories;
  - Municipal Accountant to maintain Supplies Ledger Cards (SLC) for
inventories;
  - Acting GSO and the Municipal Accountant to reconcile their records regularly;
and
  - Municipal Accountant to take up the necessary entries to adjust the affected
accounts, if warranted.
